      "description": "Shop Etsy—your global marketplace for original items made, handpicked, and designed by real people for all budgets. Explore everything from vintage treasures and trending style pieces to personalized jewelry and custom home decor. Get offers and deals on one-of-a-kind items from small shops, chat with Etsy sellers, track your orders, and more.\n \nDownload today and shop unique pieces from our community of sellers.\n \nDiscover Special\nExplore over 15+ categories of original items from all over the world, including:\n• Home Goods & Decor: Find furniture or new prints to style your space, and give the perfect housewarming gifts with pieces like handmade glassware sets or a custom dining table.\n• New & Vintage Clothes: Shop clothing for men, women, and children and elevate your personal wardrobe.*\n• Jewelry & Accessories: Accessorize your looks with unique and handmade rings, earrings, and necklaces.\n• Original Art & Collectibles: Pick up finds from around the world, like Turkish pottery and Portuguese ceramics.\n• DIY Ideas: Get all the supplies and craft kits you need to throw a themed party or learn a new hobby.\n\nSave More with the Etsy app\nShop top offers and deals from small shops with curated selections of items on sale from sellers you love. Plus, stay updated on sales for your favorite pieces with push notifications!\n\nOne-of-a-Kind Finds\nPersonalize clothes, decor, and style essentials to make your gifts one-of-a-kind. Customization knows no bounds with Etsy.\n\nSearch by Image\nLooking for something similar? Explore items that look like your favorite pieces so you can discover even more one-of-a-kind finds.\n\nEasily Track Your Order\nTrack gifts and shipments with real-time updates on your order status—including customized notifications to your taste. Chat with sellers, ask questions and stay in-the-know on your order on the app.\n\nSafe & Seamless Checkout\nShop safely with secure payments, including credit/debit, Etsy gift cards, Paypal, Klarna, and quick purchases with Apple Pay. \n\nFavorite, Organize & Create Lists\nFavorite shops, save items, and organize your pieces in collections for future inspiration. Or, create a gift list of your favorite items and save special occasions for helpful reminders.\n\nGift Easy\nNeed help picking out a gift or shopping last minute? Etsy has you covered. Shop gift guides for every occasion, or send a custom gift teaser to give people a sneak peek at the present on the way, including gifts for:\n• Birthdays\n• Anniversaries\n• Engagements\n• Weddings\n• Holidays\n• Her, Him & Pets\n• & so much more!\n\nGet Inspired\nAccess inspiration at your fingertips with the Etsy app. Browse new and trending items or shop curated collections and “new picks for you” to discover the latest in home, style, and more.\n\nDiscover something special for every occasion from a global community of talented sellers—from clothing and furniture to art, decor, and more. Download today.\n \n*Etsy does not evaluate vintage items’ condition and authenticity.",
